<h3 id="redis-module-설정">Redis module 설정</h3>

<p>Redis가 설치되어 있는 VM에 진행</p>

<h4 id="모듈-활성화-1">모듈 활성화</h4>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>metricbeat modules <span class="nb">enable </span>redis
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="모듈-설정-1">모듈 설정</h4>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/etc/metricbeat/modules.d/redis.yml</code> 수정</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">module</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">redis</span>
  <span class="na">metricsets</span><span class="pi">:</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">info</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">keyspace</span>
  <span class="na">period</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">10s</span>

  <span class="na">hosts</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="pi">[</span><span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">127.0.0.1:6379"</span><span class="pi">]</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<blockquote>
  <p>ref: <a href="https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/beats/metricbeat/7.x/metricbeat-module-redis.html">https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/beats/metricbeat/7.x/metricbeat-module-redis.html</a></p>
</blockquote>

