<h3 id="kafka-module-설정">Kafka module 설정</h3>

<p>Kafka가 설치되어 있는 VM에 진행</p>

<h4 id="모듈-활성화-5">모듈 활성화</h4>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>metricbeat modules <span class="nb">enable </span>kafka
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="모듈-설정-5">모듈 설정</h4>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/etc/metricbeat/modules.d/kafka.yml</code> 수정</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">module</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">kafka</span>
  <span class="na">metricsets</span><span class="pi">:</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">partition</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">consumergroup</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">broker</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">consumer</span>
    <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="s">producer</span>
  <span class="na">period</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">10s</span>
  <span class="na">hosts</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="pi">[</span><span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">localhost:9092"</span><span class="pi">]</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<blockquote>
  <p>ref: <a href="https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/beats/metricbeat/7.x/metricbeat-module-kafka.html">https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/beats/metricbeat/7.x/metricbeat-module-kafka.html</a></p>
</blockquote>

<h4 id="kafka-with-jolokia">Kafka with jolokia</h4>

<p>broker, consumer, producer metricset을 가져오려면 jolokia를 이용하여 jmx 모니터링하여야한다.</p>

<p>kafka에 jolokia가 javaagent로 붙어서 jvm 위에 실행</p>

<p><a href="https://dev.to/martinhynar/monitoring-kafka-brokers-using-jolokia-metricbeat-and-elasticsearch-5678">https://dev.to/martinhynar/monitoring-kafka-brokers-using-jolokia-metricbeat-and-elasticsearch-5678</a> 참조</p>

