<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">module</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">zookeeper</span>
  <span class="na">metricsets</span><span class="pi">:</span>
