<hr />
<h2 id="metricbeat-setup">Metricbeat setup</h2>
<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># dashboard 생성을 위해 /usr/share/metricbeat 이동하여 실행</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">cd</span> /usr/share/metricbeat

<span class="c"># -e 옵션으로 error 여부를 stdout 으로 출력. log에서 host에 정상 접속 했는지 확인 가능</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span>metricbeat setup <span class="nt">-e</span> <span class="nt">-c</span> /etc/metricbeat/metricbeat.yml <span class="nt">--dashboards</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>setup 완료 후 마지막 문장에 dashboard가 정상 로딩된 것을 확인
<img src="/assets/img/contents/emm-10.png" alt="emm-10.png" /></p>

<hr />
<h2 id="metricbeat-구동">Metricbeat 구동</h2>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>systemctl start metricbeat.service
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="metricbeat-log-확인">Metricbeat log 확인</h2>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>journalctl <span class="nt">-u</span> metricbeat
</code></pre></div></div>

